titleInfo.title: Hat World, Inc. v. Kelly
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge Edmund F. Brennan on 7/10/12 ORDERING that the motion for expedited discovery, 17 is granted in part and denied in part, with each party to bear its own costs. Defendant shall respond to the discovery ordered at the hearing on a rolling basis, but no later than 7/23/12. Additionally, the parties shall meet and confer to agree on a date during the week of 7/16/12 for defendant to depose a Rule 30(b)(6) representative designated by plaintiff, and a date during the week of 7/23/12 for plaintiff to depose defendant. Each deposition shall last no more than two hours and shall be held in San Francisco (plaintiff's 30(b)(6) representative shall be deposed at defense counsel's offices and defendant shall be deposed at plaintiff's counsel's offices). (Becknal, R)
